screen_desc: The screenshot shows a mobile app interface prompting the user to select a preferred payment method. The options available are "Credit or Debit Card," "Google Pay," and "Gift Card." There is a "Skip" option at the top right corner. Below, a message asks, "Are you sure? You won't be able to request a ride without adding a payment method." Two buttons are provided: "Add Payment Method Now" and "Do it Later." The time displayed at the top is 11:02 AM, and the battery is fully charged.
